{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":956,"text":"What are you doing on this stage"},{"time":5390,"text":"in front of all these people?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":8532,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":9930,"text":"Run!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":11105,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":12132,"text":"Run now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14734,"text":"That's the voice of my anxiety talking."},{"time":18539,"text":"Even when there's absolutely\nnothing wrong,"},{"time":21499,"text":"I sometimes get\nthis overwhelming sense of doom,"},{"time":25482,"text":"like danger is lurking\njust around the corner."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29057,"text":"You see, a few years ago,"},{"time":31197,"text":"I was diagnosed with generalized anxiety"},{"time":33718,"text":"and depression --"},{"time":35289,"text":"two conditions that often go hand in hand."},{"time":38073,"text":"Now, there was a time\nI wouldn't have told anybody,"},{"time":42362,"text":"especially not in front of a big audience."},{"time":44846,"text":"As a black woman,"},{"time":46397,"text":"I've had to develop\nextraordinary resilience to succeed."},{"time":50061,"text":"And like most people in my community,"},{"time":52064,"text":"I had the misconception that depression\nwas a sign of weakness,"},{"time":55896,"text":"a character flaw."},{"time":57456,"text":"But I wasn't weak;"},{"time":59054,"text":"I was a high achiever."},{"time":60925,"text":"I'd earned a Master's degree\nin Media Studies"},{"time":63152,"text":"and had a string of high-profile jobs\nin the film and television industries."},{"time":67734,"text":"I'd even won two Emmy Awards\nfor my hard work."},{"time":71436,"text":"Sure, I was totally spent,"},{"time":74476,"text":"I lacked interest in things\nI used to enjoy,"},{"time":77170,"text":"barely ate,"},{"time":78492,"text":"struggled with insomnia"},{"time":80419,"text":"and felt isolated and depleted."},{"time":83562,"text":"But depressed?"},{"time":84938,"text":"No, not me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":87921,"text":"It took weeks before I could admit it,"},{"time":90151,"text":"but the doctor was right:"},{"time":91604,"text":"I was depressed."},{"time":93411,"text":"Still, I didn't tell anybody\nabout my diagnosis."},{"time":97522,"text":"I was too ashamed."},{"time":99159,"text":"I didn't think I had the right\nto be depressed."},{"time":102418,"text":"I had a privileged life"},{"time":104072,"text":"with a loving family\nand a successful career."},{"time":107708,"text":"And when I thought about\nthe unspeakable horrors"},{"time":110324,"text":"that my ancestors\nhad been through in this country"},{"time":112836,"text":"so that I could have it better,"},{"time":114828,"text":"my shame grew even deeper."},{"time":116980,"text":"I was standing on their shoulders."},{"time":119097,"text":"How could I let them down?"},{"time":121382,"text":"I would hold my head up,"},{"time":123459,"text":"put a smile on my face"},{"time":125843,"text":"and never tell a soul."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130466,"text":"On July 4, 2013,"},{"time":134479,"text":"my world came crashing in on me."},{"time":137399,"text":"That was the day I got\na phone call from my mom"},{"time":140324,"text":"telling me that my 22-year-old nephew,\nPaul, had ended his life,"},{"time":144538,"text":"after years of battling\ndepression and anxiety."},{"time":148668,"text":"There are no words that can describe\nthe devastation I felt."},{"time":152667,"text":"Paul and I were very close,"},{"time":153985,"text":"but I had no idea he was in so much pain."},{"time":156696,"text":"Neither one of us had ever talked\nto the other about our struggles."},{"time":160278,"text":"The shame and stigma kept us both silent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164161,"text":"Now, my way of dealing with adversity\nis to face it head on,"},{"time":168188,"text":"so I spent the next two years\nresearching depression and anxiety,"},{"time":171370,"text":"and what I found was mind-blowing."},{"time":174764,"text":"The World Health Organization reports"},{"time":176762,"text":"that depression is the leading cause\nof sickness and disability"},{"time":182010,"text":"in the world."},{"time":184039,"text":"While the exact cause\nof depression isn't clear,"},{"time":187054,"text":"research suggests\nthat most mental disorders develop,"},{"time":190176,"text":"at least in part,"},{"time":191927,"text":"because of a chemical\nimbalance in the brain,"},{"time":194606,"text":"and/or an underlying\ngenetic predisposition."},{"time":199041,"text":"So you can't just shake it off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202907,"text":"For black Americans,"},{"time":204662,"text":"stressors like racism\nand socioeconomic disparities"},{"time":208742,"text":"put them at a 20 percent greater risk\nof developing a mental disorder,"},{"time":213806,"text":"yet they seek mental health services"},{"time":216242,"text":"at about half the rate of white Americans."},{"time":219544,"text":"One reason is the stigma,"},{"time":222418,"text":"with 63 percent of black Americans\nmistaking depression for a weakness."},{"time":229603,"text":"Sadly, the suicide rate\namong black children"},{"time":233885,"text":"has doubled in the past 20 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237843,"text":"Now, here's the good news:"},{"time":240603,"text":"seventy percent of people\nstruggling with depression will improve"},{"time":244909,"text":"with therapy, treatment and medication."},{"time":249458,"text":"Armed with this information,"},{"time":251144,"text":"I made a decision:"},{"time":252875,"text":"I wasn't going to be silent anymore."},{"time":256740,"text":"With my family's blessing,"},{"time":258567,"text":"I would share our story"},{"time":260484,"text":"in hopes of sparking\na national conversation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264140,"text":"A friend, Kelly Pierre-Louis, said,"},{"time":266935,"text":"\"Being strong is killing us.\""},{"time":270743,"text":"She's right."},{"time":272186,"text":"We have got to retire\nthose tired, old narratives"},{"time":276232,"text":"of the strong black woman"},{"time":277811,"text":"and the super-masculine black man,"},{"time":280045,"text":"who, no matter how many times\nthey get knocked down,"},{"time":282989,"text":"just shake it off and soldier on."},{"time":285770,"text":"Having feelings isn't a sign of weakness."},{"time":290521,"text":"Feelings mean we're human."},{"time":292850,"text":"And when we deny our humanity,"},{"time":294893,"text":"it leaves us feeling empty inside,"},{"time":297033,"text":"searching for ways to self-medicate\nin order to fill the void."},{"time":300585,"text":"My drug was high achievement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304371,"text":"These days, I share my story openly,"},{"time":307696,"text":"and I ask others to share theirs, too."},{"time":310406,"text":"I believe that's what it takes"},{"time":311878,"text":"to help people who may\nbe suffering in silence"},{"time":314497,"text":"to know that they are not alone"},{"time":316730,"text":"and to know that with help,"},{"time":318439,"text":"they can heal."},{"time":319804,"text":"Now, I still have my struggles,"},{"time":321993,"text":"particularly with the anxiety,"},{"time":324305,"text":"but I'm able to manage it"},{"time":325932,"text":"through daily mediation,\nyoga and a relatively healthy diet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330830,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":331922,"text":"If I feel like things\nare starting to spiral,"},{"time":334168,"text":"I make an appointment to see my therapist,"},{"time":336236,"text":"a dynamic black woman\nnamed Dawn Armstrong,"},{"time":339323,"text":"who has a great sense of humor"},{"time":341320,"text":"and a familiarity that I find comforting."},{"time":345126,"text":"I will always regret"},{"time":347390,"text":"that I couldn't be there for my nephew."},{"time":350226,"text":"But my sincerest hope"},{"time":352695,"text":"is that I can inspire others\nwith the lesson that I've learned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359182,"text":"Life is beautiful."},{"time":362646,"text":"Sometimes it's messy,"},{"time":364232,"text":"and it's always unpredictable."},{"time":367034,"text":"But it will all be OK"},{"time":368261,"text":"when you have your support system\nto help you through it."},{"time":371513,"text":"I hope that if your burden gets too heavy,"},{"time":373958,"text":"you'll ask for a hand, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375688,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":376879,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}